<li>Brave Keyword: Battlefield Scan is missing. </li>
<li>Stealth Keyword: Battlefield Scan and Hiding Spot are missing. </li>
<li>You can't swipe between cards in the Stratagem section. </li>
<li>If you add Arcee to your team, then switch to the game mode and try to convert her to bot-mode, the game offers a feature to Form Sergeant Six-Gun. When you do this you get Raider Brunt. </li>
<li>If you add the two pieces of Raider Brunt to your deck, or the two pieces of Sergeant Six-Gun, then switch to game mode, then switch back and remove them, you will have gained a 11 or 9 stars that can't be removed. </li>
</ol>

